main event: A large white object was sighted at arm's length in Marshalltown, Iowa on 2% Oct 55.
interesting points: The sighting was categorized as 'Visual' and reported by a civilian., The object was described as round and white, roughly the size of a basketball., The object was seen with binoculars during dusk., The report suggests the object may have been a balloon launched from General Mills., The conclusion states there was insufficient data for evaluation.
